---
title: 'Chopped Cheese' Chorizo Quesadillas with Potato Wedges and Honey-Garlic Dijonnaise
description: Tonight's dinner is a fun and flavourful twist on a classic Harlem bodega sandwich known as a 'chopped cheese.' Savoury ground chorizo is topped with sharp cheddar and juicy tomatoes before getting tucked into a tortilla shell. It's served with potato wedges and a honey-garlic Dijonnaise sauce.
